data.description: Welcome home! This well cared for home has a newer pool that is waiting for you to cool off this summer! This home has beautiful vaulted ceilings in an open front living room. Tile through out the living area makes for easy cleaning! Enjoy your gatherings off your pool, covered patio and turf flowing into your updated modern kitchen with newer appliances and open family, dining room. This beautiful home has a downstairs bedroom and bathroom, great for guests! Upstairs there is a loft area for a play space or office,  2 more secondary bedrooms  and a shared bathroom. The primary bedroom and primary bathroom overlook the sparkling pool on the back of the home. Solar panels will help you save on electric in the AZ heat!
